Following TDD :
Write tests for use-case
Extend code as required
There are 3 fundamental use-cases of this app -
 1) Get Albums
 2) Save Image
 3) Get Images in an album


1) Saving image :-
 - Input -> image
 - Output -> Saved image (success) | error in the process of saving it (failure)

2) Getting albums :-
 - Input -> None
 - Output -> List of Albums (first_image, album_id) | error in the process of retrieving them | No albums

3) Get images of an album :-
 - Input -> album Id
 - Output -> Images of album | error if album doesn't exist | error in the process of retrieval